{
  "text": "Several studies [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] have suggested that DC provide naive T cells with all the necessary signals required for activation 1 Abbreviations used in this paper . CI, chemotaxis index ; CS, contact sensitivity; DC, dendritic cell; DNBS, 2,4-dinitro benzene sulfonic acid ; DTH, delayed-type hypersensitivity; fmlp, formyl peptide; HSA, heat stable antigen; ICAM-1, intracellular adhesion molecule 1; MCP-1, macrophage chemotactic protein 1 ; MIP-la, macrophage inflammatory protein la ; PAF, platelet-activating factor ; PI, phagocytosis index; rm, recombinant mouse; SpWMb, spermwhale myoglobin .",
